data.description: This Beautiful Home will give you the Wow factor from the time you enter in until you leave!!! This spacious 3 Bedroom 2 full bath with open floor plan have plenty of space for gatherings inside and out. Stainless Steel appliances, granite countertops in kitchen and bath, Ceramic Tile flooring in wet areas, wood floors in living room and carpet in bedroom, Island, Crown Moulding and much more. It won't compare to any other properties you have seen thus far. Schedule your showings today!!
